  "title": "Technical Services Technician (Full-time) | Up to $2900",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br />Join a leading <strong>contact lens manufacturing facility</strong> in Singapore, the first of its kind outside Japan for daily disposable lenses. We are looking for <strong>Technical Service Technicians</strong> to play a key role in maintaining operational efficiency and ensuring product quality through equipment maintenance and troubleshooting.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Operate manufacturing equipment to meet production schedules and targets.</p></li><li><p>Provide technical support and troubleshoot equipment to meet quality standards.</p></li><li><p>Perform daily and monthly preventive maintenance to maintain equipment reliability.</p></li><li><p>Participate actively in workplace safety initiatives and quality improvement projects.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>NITEC in any <strong>Engineering discipline</strong> (Mechanical, Mechatronics, Robotics preferred).</p></li><li><p>Ability to read and understand <strong>electrical and mechanical diagrams</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Willing to work <strong>12-hour shifts</strong> with overtime flexibility.</p></li><li><p>Able to lift <strong>10–15 kg</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working in a <strong>controlled manufacturing environment</strong>.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Shift Details:</strong></p><ul><li><p>12-hour shift based on a <strong>4-3-3-4 work-rest cycle</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Assigned to <strong>Sunday Night Shift</strong>: 7:45 PM – 7:55 AM.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><ul><li><p>Hands-on experience with <strong>advanced manufacturing equipment</strong>.</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to <strong>develop technical skills</strong> in a high-precision production environment.</p></li><li><p>Be part of a <strong>team driving innovation</strong> in healthcare manufacturing.<br /></p><p>📩 <strong>Apply Now</strong></p><p>Send your resume (MS\nWord format) to:</p><p>📱 WhatsApp / Telegram: 8509 0409</p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary in your application.</p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>—</p><p>Annie Hoang (R25158747)</p><p>CREW by HRnet |HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd </p><p>EA24C2435</p></li></ul>",
